---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import ChangelogEntry from "../components/ChangelogEntry.astro"
---

<Layout
  title="Changelog — Botyoo"
  description="Track every update we ship to Botyoo, including Instagram automation enhancements and platform improvements."
>
  <main
    class="mx-auto mt-36 max-w-3xl px-3 animate-[slide-up-fade_600ms_both]"
  >
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1
        class="py-2 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-foreground sm:text-5xl"
      >
        Changelog
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground text-balance">
        Keep yourself informed about the most recent additions and improvements
        we've made to Botyoo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-28">
      <ChangelogEntry version="v1.1.0" date="July 8, 2024">
        <h2>New Analytics Dashboard & Advanced Automation</h2>
        <p>
          We're excited to introduce our comprehensive analytics suite that
          provides deep insights into your Instagram DM performance, along with
          powerful new automation features that enhance follower engagement.
        </p>

        <img src="/changelog/v317.webp" alt="New analytics dashboard" width="1200" height="675" />

        <h3>New & Improved:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Analytics Dashboard:</strong> Track conversion rates,
            response times, and engagement metrics for all your automated DM
            conversations.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Follow Verification:</strong> New intelligent system that
            automatically verifies followers before sending premium content or
            special offers.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Conditional Responses:</strong> Create branching
            conversation paths based on user responses for more natural
            interactions.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>A/B Testing:</strong> Compare different message templates
            to determine which performs best for your specific audience.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Performance Reports:</strong> Receive weekly email reports
            with key metrics and recommendations for optimizing your DM
            strategy.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Fixes:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Message Queue:</strong> Fixed issues with message delivery
            during peak Instagram usage times.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Template Editor:</strong> Improved formatting options when
            creating multi-part automated messages.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Notification System:</strong> Enhanced reliability of
            real-time alerts for high-priority DM interactions.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Mobile Interface:</strong> Resolved display issues on
            smaller screens when viewing analytics charts.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>API Integration:</strong> Fixed connection stability with
            Instagram's messaging API during rate limit periods.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          For more information on how to leverage these new analytics features,
          check out our <a href="#">updated documentation</a>.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>

      <ChangelogEntry version="v1.0.0" date="June 15, 2024">
        <h2>Instagram DM Automation MVP Release</h2>
        <p>
          We're thrilled to announce the launch of our Instagram DM Automation
          platform. This initial release provides businesses and creators with
          essential tools to automate responses, engage followers, and convert
          comments to leads.
        </p>

        <img src="/changelog/v316.png" alt="MVP release" width="1200" height="675" />

        <h3>Core Features:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Automated Responses:</strong> Set up instant replies to
            common questions and inquiries in your Instagram DMs.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Comment-to-DM Conversion:</strong> Automatically invite
            users who comment on your posts to continue the conversation in
            DMs.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Message Templates:</strong> Create and save customizable
            message templates for different scenarios and audience segments.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Simple Rules Engine:</strong> Define basic conditions for
            when and how your automation responds to different types of
            messages.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Basic Analytics:</strong> Track message volume, response
            rates, and basic engagement metrics.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Instagram Integration:</strong> Seamless connection with
            your Instagram Business or Creator account.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>User Management:</strong> Add team members with different
            permission levels to manage your DM automation.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Getting Started:</h3>
        <p>
          To begin automating your Instagram DMs, simply connect your Instagram
          account through our secure authentication process, create your first
          message templates, and set up basic automation rules.
        </p>
        <p>
          For detailed setup instructions, check out our <a href="#"
            >quickstart guide</a
          > or contact our support team for personalized onboarding assistance.
        </p>
      </ChangelogEntry>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  @keyframes slide-up-fade {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>
